Hi Jos?,

See help(forest.rma) and in particular the 'order' argument. For example:

library(metafor)

dat <- data.frame(yi = c(.43, .12, .32, .02),
                  vi = rep(.01, 4))

res <- rma(yi, vi, data=dat)
forest(res)
forest(res, order="obs")

Best,
Wolfgang

