Dear Erika

Welcome to one of life's great challenges, tuning graphics in R. In this 
case I think you need to adjust the ylim parameter to forest(). If you 
store the result of forest and then print it you will see the defaults 
it chose and you can then engage in a process of trial and error to get 
the spacing you need.

Michael

